            F1 di <a href="https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grand_Prix_F1_Amerika_Serikat_2007">GP AS 2007</a> berasam tim <a href="https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/BMW_dalam_Formula_Satu">BMW
                Sauber</a> </div>
